<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>TSI 01-08-08 - Dual Drive Cab Throttle Position Harness for Converting 2000, 4000, 4300, 4400, and 7400
        Models to both Left and Right Hand Drive
    </stitle>
    <tsi id="tsi010808" tsitype="truck">
        <tsinumber>01-08-08</tsinumber>
        <tsidate>November, 2001</tsidate>
        <subjectfile>ELECTRICAL</subjectfile>
        <subjectgroup>
            <subject>Dual Drive Cab Throttle Position Harness for Converting 2000, 4000, 4300, 4400, and 7400 Models to
                both Left and Right Hand Drive
            </subject>
        </subjectgroup>
        <apply>
            <configure>
                <truckmodelgroup/>

                <truckmodel>2000</truckmodel>
                <truckmodel>4000</truckmodel>
                <truckmodel>4300</truckmodel>
                <truckmodel>4400</truckmodel>
                <truckmodel>7400</truckmodel>
            </configure>
        </apply>
        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>International has developed a throttle position harness to assist in the conversion of 2000, 4000,
                    4300 and 4400 Models to both left and right hand drive. The new harness eliminates the need to cut
                    and splice into the existing cab harness to connect the electronic throttle position sensor.
                </para>
                <para>Two versions of the harness are available through International Dealers or International Parts
                    Distribution Centers: Harness Part Number 2506825C91 includes a manual switch for left or right hand
                    drive operation, and Harness Part number 2505751C91 utilizes a diode to automatically switch to left
                    or right hand drive.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
